About
Peak is an independent, comprehensive and objective advisory firm providing professional management services in the financial markets.








Our Team
Because every investor has a unique set of needs, goals and priorities, we have assembled a diverse team of investment advisors who see the market from all sides. While we understand that our services are not a universal solution to all portfolio management needs, we have built our business on principles that we believe position us to provide a superior solution to a select group of investors. The members of our team have earned internationally recognized certifications including CFA, CFP, CPA and FRM.  
Learn more about Our Team







A Relationship of Trust
The relationship that you have with your financial advisory firm should be one based on trust. 
